id%3DEN1067&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=c64978b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_list?id=EN1067</a><br />\nPlease sign to request the house to treat BN(O)(HKers) equally in immigration and the granting of working visa as British Citizens, and include BN(O) in the potential Freedom of Movement with the United Kingdom. </blockquote>"},{"pid":"59f8aadc0afde1803f2c16d6c00a3b1bc0204a15","tid":1675150,"uid":44869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d726a2583d548741d28e25c1cc883fa4d20cfe14","tid":1675150,"uid":305335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56ee3051b704b415bcb4f0430aeb7d3021415e98","tid":1675150,"uid":44869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有經驗點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38qr5Vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38qr5Vc.jpg&h=17241b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDWiW1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDWiW1X.jpg&h=69d4fa38&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"點解佢會整親？ 唔識出聲嘅動物更要小心留意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"我唔係主人，早兩日先寄養住係我屋企。<br />\n今日先留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個位似整親定係有病導致<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e450e305c9604d4c18e82b8ffc74e905b16850","tid":1675150,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjEwyoq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjEwyoq.gif&h=17384b8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7d984546e4431b52207f1a56f89e85d813a40d5","tid":1675150,"uid":44869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b023613c81eb49fbdd3db1132d2e081445a8464","tid":1675150